&lt;h2&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About the Role:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The Associate Account Manager is responsible for owning and growing developing accounts within a defined market and business channel. This role supports account execution, sales performance, and cross-functional delivery in partnership with internal teams. The Associate Manager owns their account performance while also supporting broader commercial activities and accounts across the market.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
