&lt;li&gt;Strong organizational and administrative skills&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Comfort with Excel, presentations, and CRM tools&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Eager to learn and grow within commercial environment&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Fluent in English and key market specific languages&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
